{"type":"text","timestamp":1775871607356,"sessionID":"ses_285cf3c6dffe1i584ImzHLgGbX","part":{"id":"prt_d7a321c1b001Xtnps8B8LF2OJr","messageID":"msg_d7a31f879001qN4G3ZIYPVfAxn","sessionID":"ses_285cf3c6dffe1i584ImzHLgGbX","type":"text","text":"## ✅ Verification Complete: AR-024 DockerService Encapsulation\n\n### Summary\nAll requirements from the spec have been successfully met. Tests are passing (45/45, 2 skipped). Coverage is 98%.\n\n### ✅ Requirements Verification\n\n**1. Package Layout** ✅\n- `agentcube/services/docker_service.py` exists and contains `DockerService` class\n- Exported from `agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n- Matches design spec structure\n\n**2. API Contract** ✅\nAll required methods implemented with correct signatures:\n\n| Method | Status | Notes |\n|--------|--------|-------|\n| `__init__(verbose: bool = False)` | ✅ | Lazy initialization of Docker client |\n| `check_docker_available() -> bool` | ✅ | Non-exception based check |\n| `build_image(...)` | ✅ | Includes path validation, build args, build_time |\n| `get_image_info(image_name: str)` | ✅ | Returns dict with image_name, image_id, image_size, size_bytes |\n| `push_image(...)` | ✅ | Supports registry_url, authentication, secure password handling |\n| `remove_image(image_name, force=True)` | ✅ | Non-exception based for safe cleanup |\n\n**3. Private Helper Methods** ✅\n- `_docker_login_sdk(...)` - Secure registry authentication\n- `_tag_image_sdk(...)` - Image tagging\n- `_format_size(...)` - Human-readable size formatting\n- `_validate_build_paths(...)` - Security path validation (prevents directory traversal)\n\n**4. Integration** ✅\n- `BuildRuntime` uses `DockerService.build_image()` (build_runtime.py:104-110)\n- `PublishRuntime` uses `DockerService.push_image()` (publish_runtime.py:89-94)\n- Both pass `verbose` flag correctly\n\n**5. Test Coverage** ✅\n```\n45 passed, 2 skipped (integration tests require Docker daemon)\nCoverage: 98% for docker_service.py\n```\n\n**6. Code Quality** ✅\n- ✅ Flake8: Passes (fixed minor newline issue)\n- ✅ Mypy: No type errors in docker_service.py\n- ✅ Follows PEP 8 conventions\n\n**7. Security** ✅\n- Passwords never logged (docker_service.py:239-240)\n- Path resolution prevents directory traversal (docker_service.py:147-158)\n- Proper exception handling and error messages\n\n### Implementation Details\n\n**Location**: `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/docker_service.py:1-330`\n\n**Key Features**:\n- Lazy client initialization (property-based)\n- Comprehensive error handling (RuntimeError, FileNotFoundError, ValueError)\n- Path validation with security checks\n- Verbose logging support\n- Build arguments for proxy configuration\n- Registry authentication support\n- Image ID truncation to 12 characters\n\n### Minor Fix Applied\n- Added missing newline at end of file to satisfy flake8 W292\n\n### Status\n**READY FOR PRODUCTION** ✅\n\nThe DockerService implementation fully complies with AR-024 specifications, is well-tested (98% coverage), properly integrated with BuildRuntime and PublishRuntime, and follows security best practices.","time":{"start":1775871607353,"end":1775871607353}}}
